Electrical Installation Inspection
https://services.clp.com.hk/en/appointment-for-installation-inspection/index.aspx
Required for new supply (no meter) and change of load for RT and NRT.
For new move in account, CLP needs to check equipment to see if it meets wiring regulations before we provide electricity. If the meter already exists, don’t need to make this appointment.
Only needed for new buildings etc, or change of load.

Bill notifications
 
Bill is ready alert
https://clp.com.hk/en/customer-service/billing/billing-value-added-service/bill-payment-reminder
Ebill notification -> Service Application -> Change billing method (Drop paper bill)
Bill is ready -> Setting Change -> No change to billing method (only app push notification)
- App push notification: Hard copy bill customers only can receive push notification if they turn on in app setting, we will not allow them to choose SMS as not cost justified and can’t drive these hard copy bill customers to go ebill
- Email notification = ebill notification
- No SMS notification for cost consideration (To be removed by Nov)
